{"tid":1486168,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］港鐵明日（19號）罷工.","createTime":"2019-08-18T19:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T19:32:40.000Z","uid":219147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a20f9b09f254db82156834cf5e78b90094b8abad","tid":1486168,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:18:12.000Z","msg":"700名港鐵車長及列車員工督察早前聯署，要求港鐵譴責警方各種影響鐵路安全的行為。有份聯署的港鐵資深車長、葵青區區議員梁志成表示，部分車長將響應於周一(19日)自發罷工，要求公司回應訴求。 <br />\n<br />\n梁表示，活動沒有大台，罷工方式將分為「缺勤」及「靜坐不開車」兩種，估計有約200名車長參與。他指車長們希望公司譴責警隊，但他認為當務之急是要政府「做嘢」，保障鐵路乘客及車長安全，故已去信運輸及房屋局局長陳帆要求回覆。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Qo7FHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Qo7FHg.png&h=a41daa57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b13b253b94c13e7e242ce6754dbd5f45df01ff4","tid":1486168,"uid":241458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:18:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有人諗住聽朝0715塞鐵，好可能會spin走咗車長罷工嘅事，希望深水埗手足聽朝去勸下佢地<br />\n<br />\n佢地個group block咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/mtrisdangerous\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmtrisdangerous&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsiWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=e4106f6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/mtrisdangerous</a>"},{"pid":"9520c58e318f19c910b9c4401822ba2bf3564ff9","tid":1486168,"uid":162422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f2191c6377c36ac5aa88d9ea09d4ef4962557e","tid":1486168,"uid":145664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b13b253b94c13e7e242ce6754dbd5f45df01ff4","tid":1486168,"uid":241458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:18:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有人諗住聽朝0715塞鐵，好可能會spin走咗車長罷工嘅事，希